data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Del Lago. This is a beautifully remodeled home, nestled above the Vineyard Golf Course, with incredible views! Enter into the living room area boasting a 2-story high vaulted ceiling, beautiful vinyl wood-like flooring, loaded with windows radiating in natural lighting. Both the living room and dining room enjoy the extremely high ceiling openness.  As you work your way toward the kitchen, it is delightfully upgraded with modern shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, multi-colored tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. Beautifully coordinated with colors and style.  The L-shaped peninsula is open to the family room which looks out west toward the majestic golf course view. The fireplace has been upgraded to flow with the color scheme.  The Master Bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor looking out the expansive golf course views with a stunning master bathroom that was just recently remodeled. For those who have EVs or just love pulling energy from the sun instead of the grid, this home is equipped with 18 solar panels on the roof, plus 2 Tesla 13.5 kWh Powerwalls. Conveniently close to the mall, shopping, Lake Hodges, freeway, and schools.Welcome to the gated community of Del Lago.
